snippet: QUEENS COUNTY FAIR.--We have on hand a report of the Queens County Agricultural Fair, held at Jamaica yesterday, and of the address of General DIX, which is crowded out, but will be given in our evening edition....
lead_paragraph: QUEENS COUNTY FAIR.--We have on hand a report of the Queens County Agricultural Fair, held at Jamaica yesterday, and of the address of General DIX, which is crowded out, but will be given in our evening edition.
